	Add HildonAppMenu::changed signal

	* hildon/hildon-app-menu.c: (hildon_app_menu_insert),
	(hildon_app_menu_add_filter), (hildon_app_menu_class_init):
	Emit a new HildonAppMenu:changed signal when there are changes in
	the menu children.

