	Use root coordinates to check if the release event happened
	outside the widget.

	* src/hildon-app-menu.c
	(hildon_app_menu_button_release):
	Remove unnecessary check

	* examples/hildon-app-menu-example.c
	(button_clicked):
	Add cast to fix warning

